{"tid":1490962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳街坊：「差佬嘅嘢，心照啦」","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:54:45.000Z","uid":36494,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"003e1d7670cf9e2a6f99e3d75850cfecd956c77a","tid":1490962,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"街坊楊先生凌晨有份與一眾街坊追緝兇徒，強烈<span style=\"color: red;\">批評警方查案「好懶散」</span>，指「警員攞咗把刀就離開，冇睇過CCTV，仲要係其中一個住戶報警要求睇CCTV，擾攘咗好耐」。<br />\n<br />\n街坊方先生願意接受訪問，但擔心個人安全，要求記者替他的樣貌打格，反映區內街坊人人自危。方先生對事件感到好無奈及憤怒，指現場過去一直相安無事，最多是有人將memo紙撕下。對於有人因政見問題用刀斬人，方先生稱：「嗰啲人啲思想理解唔到，亦都唔好嘗試去理解。」他亦不相信警方可以保護市民，「唔寄望，差佬拉到咪又係放，靠佢哋不如靠自己，佢哋冇乜作用」，所以建議市民「帶多啲嘢防身」。<br />\n<br />\n街坊吳先生亦要求記者替他的樣貌打格，他指經常有政見不同的人與年青人嘈交及撕memo紙，更向年青人推撞，但斬人事件則是首次，「做咗啲乜嘢，需要俾你去斬呀，係冇人性嘅人先會咁做」。<span style=\"color: red;\">吳先生亦對警方執法失去信心，「我覺得會拉到人，但唔方會用好重罪名，差佬嘅嘢，心照啦」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190820&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59951785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190820%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59951785&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6Vube6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=74d6296b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190820%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59951785&h=d67f5524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190820&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59951785</a>"},{"pid":"e744bfe3a00bec6d908431aa030961501755f034","tid":1490962,"uid":108337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1cgMEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1cgMEH.jpg&h=d8546aae&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDRQQ6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDRQQ6n.jpg&h=d40c8173&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjpyOS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\